  	<section name='Jajuk Home Page'>
  		 <p>Jajuk is a Java music organizer for all platforms. The main goal 
   		 of this project is to provide a fully-featured application to advanced 
   		 users with large or scattered music collections. Jajuk supports MP3, OGG Vorbis, AU, AIFF, WAV and SPEEX audio formats. Jajuk is a Free Software published under GPL license.</p>
		<p>Jajuk main principles are :
			<ul>
				<li>Maximum features: Jajuk is made firstly for advanced users looking for powerful functionalities</li>
				<li>Maximum portability and integration: 100% pure Java but native packaging and features like tray</li>
				<li>Maximum usability: Jajuk is designed to be intuitive, fast and provide multiple ways to perform the same operation</li>
				<li>Only for music: not a video or picture organizer</li>
			</ul>	
		</p>
		
